<p xml:id="subtitle1" begin="72572500t" end="82999582t" region="region0" style="style0">계약서?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle2" begin="89672916t" end="99265832t" region="region0" style="style0">웬 계약서?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle3" begin="125542082t" end="133883749t" region="region0" style="style0">김슬기</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle4" begin="150984166t" end="159742916t" region="region0" style="style0">오기철</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle5" begin="160577082t" end="173089582t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle6" begin="175592082t" end="191441250t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 의아한 숨소리]<br/>(상우)<br/>계약 완료</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle7" begin="202285416t" end="211461249t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>뭐지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle8" begin="235652082t" end="264847916t" region="region0" style="style0">'위 계약 조건을<br/>틀림없이 지키기 위하여'</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle9" begin="269852916t" end="289038750t" region="region0" style="style0">'본 계약서로 작성하고'</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle10" begin="307807500t" end="324490832t" region="region0" style="style0">'피로 서명을 한다'?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle11" begin="334083750t" end="343259582t" region="region0" style="style0">피?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle12" begin="359942916t" end="371204166t" region="region0" style="style0">[문손잡이가 덜그럭거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle13" begin="374123750t" end="392475416t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle14" begin="417917500t" end="427927499t" region="region0" style="style0">[문이 달칵 열린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle15" begin="439188749t" end="449198749t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구의 옅은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle16" begin="457123332t" end="476309166t" region="region0" style="style0">[삐걱거리는 효과음]<br/>[문이 덜컥 닫힌다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle17" begin="482148332t" end="504670832t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle18" begin="553886666t" end="564313750t" region="region0" style="style0">[코웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle19" begin="575575000t" end="586836250t" region="region0" style="style0">(게슈타포)<br/>봉구 선생</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle20" begin="595177916t" end="608941666t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>네, 김 선생님, 들어오세요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle21" begin="618534582t" end="640222916t" region="region0" style="style0">[문이 달칵 열린다]<br/>[게슈타포의 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle22" begin="652735416t" end="679428750t" region="region0" style="style0">(게슈타포)<br/>연애 상담해 주기로 해 놓고<br/>왜 말이 없어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle23" begin="684433750t" end="695695000t" region="region0" style="style0">지금 시간 돼?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle24" begin="696529166t" end="708207500t" region="region0" style="style0">네, 시간 됩니다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle25" begin="715715000t" end="744493750t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 자판기 커피라도 한잔하면서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle26" begin="749498750t" end="765765000t" region="region0" style="style0">대화의 장을 한번 나눠 볼까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle27" begin="773272500t" end="782865416t" region="region0" style="style0">- 그럴까요?<br/>- 응</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle28" begin="783699582t" end="795795000t" region="region0" style="style0">[게슈타포의 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle29" begin="800382916t" end="809975832t" region="region0" style="style0">네</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle30" begin="824573750t" end="834583750t" region="region0" style="style0">[코웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle31" begin="867533332t" end="877126249t" region="region0" style="style0">[문이 달칵 닫힌다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle32" begin="896729166t" end="906322082t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림이 숨을 내쉰다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle33" begin="917583332t" end="940939999t" region="region0" style="style0">[주제곡]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle34" begin="1131130000t" end="1153652500t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]<br/>[뛰어오는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle35" begin="1167833332t" end="1184099582t" region="region0" style="style0">[숨을 헐떡인다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle36" begin="1259591666t" end="1275440832t" region="region0" style="style0">[놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle37" begin="1295460832t" end="1312561250t" region="region0" style="style0">[겁먹은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle38" begin="1326325000t" end="1339254582t" region="region0" style="style0">[시연의 격한 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle39" begin="1360525832t" end="1369284582t" region="region0" style="style0">(상미)<br/>그래서?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle40" begin="1370118750t" end="1400565832t" region="region0" style="style0">그 스토커 얼굴은 봤어?<br/>어떻게 생겼는데?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle41" begin="1408073332t" end="1423088332t" region="region0" style="style0">(시연)<br/>어, 그게...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle42" begin="1427259166t" end="1446445000t" region="region0" style="style0">어두워서 나도 잘은 못 봤어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle43" begin="1451032916t" end="1474806666t" region="region0" style="style0">대충 180 정도에</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle44" begin="1480228750t" end="1498997500t" region="region0" style="style0">어, 좀 호리호리하고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle45" begin="1504002500t" end="1516932082t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 까만색 후드 티 쓰고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle46" begin="1517766250t" end="1535283750t" region="region0" style="style0">(상미)<br/>어? 딱 내 스타일인데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle47" begin="1538620416t" end="1558223332t" region="region0" style="style0">막 후드 티 벗으면<br/>존잘인 거 아니야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle48" begin="1559057500t" end="1574906666t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 존잘은 무슨<br/>[상미의 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle49" begin="1581997082t" end="1601182916t" region="region0" style="style0">반장, 넌 어떻게 생각해?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle50" begin="1617032082t" end="1649147500t" region="region0" style="style0">우선 학교에 알리고<br/>신고부터 해야 되는 거 아닌가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle51" begin="1656655000t" end="1669584582t" region="region0" style="style0">무슨 일 생기기 전에</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle52" begin="1675423750t" end="1687102082t" region="region0" style="style0">일은 무슨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle53" begin="1692941249t" end="1704202499t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 솔까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle54" begin="1705036666t" end="1726724999t" region="region0" style="style0">그런 애가 있었음<br/>벌써 우리도 봤겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle55" begin="1747996249t" end="1760091666t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>그렇지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle56" begin="1761342916t" end="1774272499t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 내가 그런 애가 있었으면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle57" begin="1775106666t" end="1798046249t" region="region0" style="style0">포토그래퍼의 눈으로<br/>샤샤샥 찍었겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle58" begin="1843925416t" end="1855186666t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>그나저나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle59" begin="1859357499t" end="1882714166t" region="region0" style="style0">남친이랑 부모님이<br/>걱정 많이 하시겠다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle60" begin="1883548332t" end="1892724166t" region="region0" style="style0">[시연의 옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle61" begin="1893558332t" end="1916914999t" region="region0" style="style0">(시연)<br/>아빠는 해외 출장 중이시고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle62" begin="1924005416t" end="1947362082t" region="region0" style="style0">엄마는 따로 살면서<br/>연락 안 한 지 좀 됐고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle63" begin="1951532916t" end="1969884582t" region="region0" style="style0">남친은 보스턴에 있고<br/>[상우의 놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle64" begin="1970718749t" end="1980311666t" region="region0" style="style0">그렇지, 뭐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle65" begin="1981562916t" end="2006170832t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>오, 보스턴?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle66" begin="2007004999t" end="2016180832t" region="region0" style="style0">[살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle67" begin="2018266249t" end="2032029999t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>전에 남친이</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle68" begin="2038286249t" end="2056637916t" region="region0" style="style0">뉴욕에 있다고 하지 않았었나?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle69" begin="2059140416t" end="2079994582t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle70" begin="2093341249t" end="2130878749t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 나 도서관에<br/>책 반납할 게 있어서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle71" begin="2142557082t" end="2155903750t" region="region0" style="style0">먼저 좀 가 볼게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle72" begin="2156737916t" end="2165913750t" region="region0" style="style0">- (시연) 미안<br/>- (별) 응</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle73" begin="2190104582t" end="2205953750t" region="region0" style="style0">참 어렵게도 산다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle74" begin="2213461250t" end="2241822916t" region="region0" style="style0">소설도 저 정도면<br/>베스트셀러급이야, 아주</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle75" begin="2282697082t" end="2295626666t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>그러니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle76" begin="2299797500t" end="2323154166t" region="region0" style="style0">소설에 등장하는 가상의 인물들은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle77" begin="2331078750t" end="2359440416t" region="region0" style="style0">각자의 역할에 따라<br/>다양한 성격을 갖고 있지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle78" begin="2363194166t" end="2374872500t" region="region0" style="style0">결국 모두</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle79" begin="2376540832t" end="2403234166t" region="region0" style="style0">'작가 한 사람의 인격을<br/>나타내는 거다'</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle80" begin="2406153750t" end="2419083332t" region="region0" style="style0">라고 볼 수 있는 거지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle81" begin="2425756666t" end="2434932500t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>쌤</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle82" begin="2441188750t" end="2452032916t" region="region0" style="style0">만약에</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle83" begin="2452867082t" end="2487067916t" region="region0" style="style0">작가가 완벽한 거짓말쟁이면<br/>어떻게 되는 거예요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle84" begin="2497077916t" end="2520434582t" region="region0" style="style0">캐릭터도 전부 거짓 아니에요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle85" begin="2528776250t" end="2545459582t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]<br/>(봉구)<br/>아...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle86" begin="2546293750t" end="2564645416t" region="region0" style="style0">창작의 궁극적 목적은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle87" begin="2568816250t" end="2596760832t" region="region0" style="style0">독자의 이목을 끌고<br/>흥미를 유발시키는 거다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle88" begin="2603851250t" end="2638052082t" region="region0" style="style0">만약에 모든 것이<br/>완벽한 거짓말이라고 해도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle89" begin="2639720416t" end="2657237916t" region="region0" style="style0">이목을 끌 수 있다면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle90" begin="2659740416t" end="2670167500t" region="region0" style="style0">그건 곧</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle91" begin="2673087082t" end="2683514166t" region="region0" style="style0">재능이며</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle92" begin="2686850832t" end="2699780416t" region="region0" style="style0">진실이 되는 거다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle93" begin="2711458750t" end="2720634582t" region="region0" style="style0">적어도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle94" begin="2728559166t" end="2744408332t" region="region0" style="style0">소설 속 세계에서는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle95" begin="2759006250t" end="2771518750t" region="region0" style="style0">자, 오늘 수업은 여기까지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle96" begin="2780694582t" end="2801548750t" region="region0" style="style0">작문 수행 평가 결과를<br/>나눠 주겠다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle97" begin="2806136666t" end="2816146666t" region="region0" style="style0">서상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle98" begin="2858272082t" end="2868282082t" region="region0" style="style0">천재수</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle99" begin="2914161250t" end="2924588332t" region="region0" style="style0">저, 선생님</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle100" begin="2930010416t" end="2951281666t" region="region0" style="style0">제 점수가<br/>좀 이상한 것 같은데요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle101" begin="2963377082t" end="2975472500t" region="region0" style="style0">네 글에는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle102" begin="2978809166t" end="2988819166t" region="region0" style="style0">마음이 없다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle103" begin="2994241250t" end="3006753750t" region="region0" style="style0">기교만 있을 뿐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle104" begin="3011758750t" end="3028859166t" region="region0" style="style0">읽는 시간조차 아까운 쓰레기다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle105" begin="3035949582t" end="3045959582t" region="region0" style="style0">어떻게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle106" begin="3051381666t" end="3061391666t" region="region0" style="style0">한번 읽어 줄까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle107" begin="3089336250t" end="3105602500t" region="region0" style="style0">[시험지를 바스락 접는다]<br/>[재수의 옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle108" begin="3123954166t" end="3133547082t" region="region0" style="style0">[혀를 찬다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle109" begin="3134381250t" end="3149813332t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 이 글은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle110" begin="3151481666t" end="3168999166t" region="region0" style="style0">상당히 마음에 드는 글이다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle111" begin="3192355832t" end="3201948750t" region="region0" style="style0">안시연</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle112" begin="3203200000t" end="3222802916t" region="region0" style="style0">[학생들의 감탄]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle113" begin="3237817916t" end="3251998750t" region="region0" style="style0">선물도 준비되어 있으니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle114" begin="3260340416t" end="3272852916t" region="region0" style="style0">이따가 상담실로 오도록</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle115" begin="3277023750t" end="3290370416t" region="region0" style="style0">[살짝 웃으며]<br/>네</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle116" begin="3302048750t" end="3313310000t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>자, 그럼<br/>[교탁을 탁 친다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle117" begin="3347093750t" end="3378792082t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 시연이한테<br/>영상 통화 한번 부탁해 볼까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle118" begin="3380877499t" end="3394641249t" region="region0" style="style0">보스턴 남친이랑</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle119" begin="3398394999t" end="3422168749t" region="region0" style="style0">(상미)<br/>드디어 보스턴 남친 목소리<br/>듣는 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle120" begin="3423002916t" end="3431344582t" region="region0" style="style0">[함께 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle121" begin="3432178749t" end="3443022916t" region="region0" style="style0">(혜민)<br/>어, 나도, 나도, 궁금해</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle122" begin="3444274166t" end="3457203749t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>그렇지, 어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle123" begin="3484731249t" end="3504751249t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle124" begin="3624037082t" end="3642388749t" region="region0" style="style0">일기장인가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle125" begin="3659072082t" end="3682845832t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 지금 가장 절실하게<br/>원하는 걸 적어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle126" begin="3687433749t" end="3697860832t" region="region0" style="style0">그럼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle127" begin="3702031666t" end="3715795416t" region="region0" style="style0">이루어지게 될 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle128" begin="3722885832t" end="3745408332t" region="region0" style="style0">그게 설령 거짓일지라도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle129" begin="3779609166t" end="3790036249t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]<br/>자</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle130" begin="3790870416t" end="3802131666t" region="region0" style="style0">[펜을 쓱 민다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle131" begin="3802965832t" end="3812141666t" region="region0" style="style0">안시연</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle132" begin="3819232082t" end="3835081249t" region="region0" style="style0">이름을 적어, 이제 네 거니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle133" begin="3851347499t" end="3862191666t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 첫 장에는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle134" begin="3865945416t" end="3885131249t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 가장 원하는 것들을 적어 봐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle135" begin="3890970416t" end="3903899999t" region="region0" style="style0">구체적일수록 좋아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle136" begin="3908070832t" end="3930176249t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 썼던 소설처럼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle137" begin="3956035416t" end="3964377082t" region="region0" style="style0">네</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle138" begin="3966879582t" end="3978974999t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>아, 아, 아니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle139" begin="4000663332t" end="4013175832t" region="region0" style="style0">이 자리에서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle140" begin="4014844166t" end="4024019999t" region="region0" style="style0">지금</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle141" begin="4030276249t" end="4052798749t" region="region0" style="style0">[난처한 숨을 내쉬며]<br/>지금 여기서요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle142" begin="4059472082t" end="4081994582t" region="region0" style="style0">[잔잔한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle143" begin="4082828749t" end="4105768332t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle144" begin="4161240416t" end="4188767916t" region="region0" style="style0">(시연)<br/>내가 지금 가장 절실하게<br/>원하는 것</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle145" begin="4226722499t" end="4242571666t" region="region0" style="style0">남자 친구 석필호</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle146" begin="4261757499t" end="4290119166t" region="region0" style="style0">지금은 머나먼 보스턴에서<br/>스터디 중</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle147" begin="4309722082t" end="4339752082t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 장신에 모델 포스의 간지남</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle148" begin="4371867500t" end="4395224166t" region="region0" style="style0">하지만 언제나 나만을 바라봐 준다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle149" begin="4408570832t" end="4436098332t" region="region0" style="style0">게다가 필호는 예술에도<br/>타고난 재능이 있다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle150" begin="4446942500t" end="4470716250t" region="region0" style="style0">기타리스트가<br/>되고 싶어 하지만...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle151" begin="4502831666t" end="4519932082t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 5년 전부터</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle152" begin="4527856666t" end="4552881666t" region="region0" style="style0">어디선가 나를 주시하는<br/>스토커가 있다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle153" begin="4569982082t" end="4592921666t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle154" begin="4634212916t" end="4647142500t" region="region0" style="style0">[시연이 깊은숨을 내뱉는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle155" begin="4655484166t" end="4665494166t" region="region0" style="style0">다 썼으면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle156" begin="4667996666t" end="4680926250t" region="region0" style="style0">일기장 놔두고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle157" begin="4685931250t" end="4695107082t" region="region0" style="style0">가 봐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle158" begin="4704282916t" end="4734312916t" region="region0" style="style0">저한테 이거<br/>선물로 준다 그러지 않으셨어요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle159" begin="4747242500t" end="4759755000t" region="region0" style="style0">그건 선물이 아니야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle160" begin="4771850416t" end="4781860416t" region="region0" style="style0">기다려 보도록</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle161" begin="4799377916t" end="4808553750t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>시연아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle162" begin="4820232082t" end="4831910416t" region="region0" style="style0">- 시연아<br/>- 어, 어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle163" begin="4832744582t" end="4846091250t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐해<br/>[시연의 멋쩍은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle164" begin="4851513332t" end="4871950416t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 오늘 남친한테</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle165" begin="4872784582t" end="4889885000t" region="region0" style="style0">영상 통화 한번<br/>걸어 보는 거 어때?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle166" begin="4900729166t" end="4919497916t" region="region0" style="style0">- (별) 어?<br/>- 아, 아니야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle167" begin="4920749166t" end="4941603332t" region="region0" style="style0">어차피 지금 시차도 안 맞아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle168" begin="4942437500t" end="4951613332t" region="region0" style="style0">아니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle169" begin="4956201250t" end="4974970000t" region="region0" style="style0">지금이 11시니까, 씁...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle170" begin="4978723750t" end="4999995000t" region="region0" style="style0">보스턴은 아마 밤 10시일걸?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle171" begin="5007919582t" end="5027105416t" region="region0" style="style0">[신비로운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle172" begin="5028773750t" end="5044205832t" region="region0" style="style0">(시연)<br/>어, 그...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle173" begin="5045457082t" end="5058386666t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 얼른</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle174" begin="5059220832t" end="5072984582t" region="region0" style="style0">전화 한번 걸어 봐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle175" begin="5076321250t" end="5093838750t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐, 시차 때문에<br/>안 된다, 어쩐다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle176" begin="5094672916t" end="5114275832t" region="region0" style="style0">그런 얘기 좀 그만하고, 응?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle177" begin="5115110000t" end="5123451666t" region="region0" style="style0">[시연의 난감한 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle178" begin="5124285832t" end="5139717916t" region="region0" style="style0">아니, 그게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle179" begin="5140552082t" end="5160572082t" region="region0" style="style0">요금도 좀 많이 나오고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle180" begin="5162240416t" end="5183094582t" region="region0" style="style0">아이, 그러지 말고 시연아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle181" begin="5184762916t" end="5194355832t" region="region0" style="style0">한 번만, 응?<br/>[학교 종소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle182" begin="5195190000t" end="5206034166t" region="region0" style="style0">[시연의 난처한 숨소리]<br/>어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle183" begin="5226888332t" end="5235647082t" region="region0" style="style0">시연아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle184" begin="5236481250t" end="5260255000t" region="region0" style="style0">다음 쉬는 시간에는 꼭 하는 거다<br/>알았지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle185" begin="5268596666t" end="5279857916t" region="region0" style="style0">[뛰어가는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle186" begin="5282777500t" end="5292370416t" region="region0" style="style0">[난처한 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle187" begin="5391636250t" end="5403314582t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>새로 온 전학생</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle188" begin="5404148750t" end="5414575832t" region="region0" style="style0">석필호다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle189" begin="5433344582t" end="5460037916t" region="region0" style="style0">필호는 미국 보스턴에서 살다 왔다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle190" begin="5461706250t" end="5492153332t" region="region0" style="style0">그렇다고 우리말이 서투르거나<br/>뭐, 그런 건 아니니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle191" begin="5496741250t" end="5523851666t" region="region0" style="style0">염려 말고 친하게 지내도록<br/>[의미심장한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle192" begin="5535947082t" end="5558052500t" region="region0" style="style0">안녕하세요, 석필호라고 합니다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle193" begin="5565977082t" end="5581409166t" region="region0" style="style0">빈자리 찾아가서 앉아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle194" begin="5631042082t" end="5653564582t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle195" begin="5717378332t" end="5732810416t" region="region0" style="style0">[학생들이 웅성거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle196" begin="5772433332t" end="5784528750t" region="region0" style="style0">(필호)<br/>오래 기다렸지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle197" begin="5810387916t" end="5822900416t" region="region0" style="style0">보고 싶었어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle198" begin="5834578750t" end="5850010832t" region="region0" style="style0">[학생들의 감탄]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle199" begin="5888382500t" end="5897975416t" region="region0" style="style0">[필호의 옅은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle200" begin="5926337082t" end="5935512916t" region="region0" style="style0">[문이 달칵 닫힌다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle201" begin="5936347082t" end="5946357082t" region="region0" style="style0">[다급한 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle202" begin="5949276666t" end="5964708750t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>노크는 기본 예의다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle203" begin="5969296666t" end="5988482500t" region="region0" style="style0">(시연)<br/>어떻게 이런<br/>말도 안 되는 일이...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle204" begin="5989316666t" end="6006417082t" region="region0" style="style0">내가 그랬잖아, 선물이라고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle205" begin="6010170832t" end="6021015000t" region="region0" style="style0">왜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle206" begin="6023517500t" end="6035612916t" region="region0" style="style0">마음에 안 들어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle207" begin="6074818750t" end="6087331250t" region="region0" style="style0">싫지는 않은가 보네</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle208" begin="6102346250t" end="6112356250t" region="region0" style="style0">(시연)<br/>지금</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle209" begin="6139466666t" end="6157818332t" region="region0" style="style0">이게 꿈인가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle210" begin="6164908750t" end="6177004166t" region="region0" style="style0">[깊은숨을 내뱉는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle211" begin="6191185000t" end="6214958750t" region="region0" style="style0">상상력 풍부한 학생이 왜 이러실까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle212" begin="6218712500t" end="6230807916t" region="region0" style="style0">내가 그랬지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle213" begin="6234978750t" end="6257501250t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 쓴 대로 이루어질 거라고<br/>[긴장되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle214" begin="6258335416t" end="6286697082t" region="region0" style="style0">그렇지만 정말로 필호가<br/>나타날 줄은 몰랐어요, 선생님</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle215" begin="6287531250t" end="6299209582t" region="region0" style="style0">[시연의 떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle216" begin="6321315000t" end="6340917916t" region="region0" style="style0">착한 학생은 선생님 말을 믿어야지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle217" begin="6349676666t" end="6358852500t" region="region0" style="style0">안시연</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle218" begin="6384711666t" end="6404314582t" region="region0" style="style0">(필호)<br/>시연이가 했던 말 중에서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle219" begin="6405148750t" end="6422249166t" region="region0" style="style0">하나만큼은 거짓말이 맞아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle220" begin="6433093332t" end="6442686250t" region="region0" style="style0">실은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle221" begin="6450610832t" end="6466042916t" region="region0" style="style0">내가 만나자고 쫓아다닌 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle222" begin="6467294166t" end="6488565416t" region="region0" style="style0">[학생들의 부러움 섞인 환호]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle223" begin="6497741250t" end="6515675832t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>어우, 닭살</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle224" begin="6527354166t" end="6537364166t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 힘겨운 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle225" begin="6538198332t" end="6561137916t" region="region0" style="style0">정말 바람직하지 않다, 정말</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle226" begin="6571147916t" end="6596590000t" region="region0" style="style0">[살짝 웃으며]<br/>왜? 좋아 보이는데?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle227" begin="6609936666t" end="6620363750t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 헛기침]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle228" begin="6623283332t" end="6636630000t" region="region0" style="style0">그럼 예림아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle229" begin="6639132500t" end="6652062082t" region="region0" style="style0">우리도 이제...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle230" begin="6652896250t" end="6669579582t" region="region0" style="style0">[살짝 웃으며]<br/>죽는다<br/>[상우의 아파하는 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle231" begin="6671665000t" end="6680840832t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우가 살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle232" begin="6681675000t" end="6694604582t" region="region0" style="style0">[별과 상미의 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle233" begin="6697107082t" end="6710870832t" region="region0" style="style0">(상미)<br/>어, 시연아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle234" begin="6711705000t" end="6742986249t" region="region0" style="style0">미안해, 그동안 잠깐<br/>오해를 했었네, 내가</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle235" begin="6744654582t" end="6768011249t" region="region0" style="style0">[살짝 웃으며]<br/>아니야, 괜찮아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle236" begin="6772599166t" end="6786362916t" region="region0" style="style0">그런데 필호</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle237" begin="6787614166t" end="6814724582t" region="region0" style="style0">장난 아니다, 부러워<br/>[함께 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle238" begin="6826402916t" end="6842669166t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>난 뭐...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle239" begin="6848091249t" end="6875618749t" region="region0" style="style0">여전히 이 상황이<br/>잘 믿기진 않지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle240" begin="6883126249t" end="6901477916t" region="region0" style="style0">어쨌든 미안했다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle241" begin="6914824582t" end="6926919999t" region="region0" style="style0">어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle242" begin="6929839582t" end="6945688749t" region="region0" style="style0">나도 사과는 받아 둘게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle243" begin="6954447499t" end="6964457499t" region="region0" style="style0">박별</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle244" begin="6976552916t" end="6986979999t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 갈게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle245" begin="6987814166t" end="7000743749t" region="region0" style="style0">가자, 가자, 가자</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle246" begin="7049125416t" end="7069562499t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle247" begin="7070396666t" end="7080823749t" region="region0" style="style0">(필호)<br/>가자, 시연아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle248" begin="7091667916t" end="7106265832t" region="region0" style="style0">어, 가자</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle249" begin="7141300832t" end="7161320832t" region="region0" style="style0">[무거운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle250" begin="7553796249t" end="7563806249t" region="region0" style="style0">시연아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle251" begin="7564640416t" end="7578404166t" region="region0" style="style0">- (시연) 응?<br/>- 너 밥은?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle252" begin="7675167499t" end="7685177499t" region="region0" style="style0">고마워</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle253" begin="7733559166t" end="7743986249t" region="region0" style="style0">그런데 말이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle254" begin="7781940832t" end="7799041249t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 이제 앞으로<br/>어떻게 되는 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle255" begin="7815724582t" end="7828654166t" region="region0" style="style0">앞으로라니?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle256" begin="7837412916t" end="7848257082t" region="region0" style="style0">네 이야기</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle257" begin="7849091249t" end="7873282082t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle258" begin="7875784582t" end="7889131249t" region="region0" style="style0">그게 무슨 말이야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle259" begin="7892467916t" end="7913739166t" region="region0" style="style0">이제 내 이야기는 다 떨어졌잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle260" begin="7917492916t" end="7937512916t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 더 좋은 이야기를 써 줘야지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle261" begin="7951693749t" end="7960869582t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle262" begin="8004663332t" end="8016758749t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>그러니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle263" begin="8025100416t" end="8040949582t" region="region0" style="style0">일기장이 필요하다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle264" begin="8046788749t" end="8056798749t" region="region0" style="style0">그거지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle265" begin="8061386666t" end="8093502082t" region="region0" style="style0">필호는 제가 일기장에<br/>적은 대로만 행동해요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle266" begin="8106848749t" end="8126034582t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 원하는 대로</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle267" begin="8128537082t" end="8145220416t" region="region0" style="style0">애들하고 오해도 풀었고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle268" begin="8146054582t" end="8160235416t" region="region0" style="style0">모든 게 이루어졌으니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle269" begin="8168577082t" end="8180255416t" region="region0" style="style0">이제 미국으로 돌려보낼까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle270" begin="8181089582t" end="8199024166t" region="region0" style="style0">[당황한 말투로]<br/>아니요, 선생님, 전...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle271" begin="8201109582t" end="8210702499t" region="region0" style="style0">선물은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle272" begin="8219461249t" end="8231139582t" region="region0" style="style0">여기까지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle273" begin="8238647082t" end="8251993749t" region="region0" style="style0">[신비로운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle274" begin="8252827916t" end="8272430832t" region="region0" style="style0">이제부터는 계약을 해야 되는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle275" begin="8276601666t" end="8289114166t" region="region0" style="style0">괜찮겠어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle276" begin="8289948332t" end="8317475832t" region="region0" style="style0">계, 계, 계약요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle277" begin="8347088749t" end="8361686666t" region="region0" style="style0">[메트로놈이 똑딱거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle278" begin="8382957916t" end="8402977916t" region="region0" style="style0">그러니까 정말 계약을 하면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle279" begin="8411319582t" end="8430922499t" region="region0" style="style0">일기장이 제 것이 된다는 거죠?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle280" begin="8449691249t" end="8463454999t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>응<br/>[신비로운 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle281" begin="8473882082t" end="8492650832t" region="region0" style="style0">(시연)<br/>아, 어떻...<br/>[시연의 놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle282" begin="8496821666t" end="8505580416t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>왜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle283" begin="8522680832t" end="8532273749t" region="region0" style="style0">[속삭이며]<br/>마저 봐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle284" begin="8568142916t" end="8589831249t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle285" begin="8619027082t" end="8629454166t" region="region0" style="style0">할게요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle286" begin="8640715416t" end="8650308332t" region="region0" style="style0">계약</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle287" begin="8664906250t" end="8673665000t" region="region0" style="style0">‘굿 초이스’</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle288" begin="8674499166t" end="8686177500t" region="region0" style="style0">[날카로운 효과음]<br/>[아파하는 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle289" begin="8756664582t" end="8782523750t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱]<br/>[기괴한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle290" begin="8804212082t" end="8814639166t" region="region0" style="style0">[쿵 하는 효과음]</p>
